{"tid":2284063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剋夫 = 劏豬凳 = 一上就死","createTime":"2020-11-13T04:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T15:40:03.000Z","uid":123774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1eaf60199b101089b2d8deb8807a0fcf1f461b7e","tid":2284063,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"所謂「劏豬凳」，就係剋夫。<br />\n<br />\n舊時豬肉佬包辦養猪、劏豬、賣肉。有張凳係劏豬時專用，行內稱爲「劏豬凳」。生歐歐嘅肥猪，一旦俾人擡上張凳，就死期到矣。於是乎，想像力豐富者將命硬女人比作「劏豬凳」，而同佢結婚嘅男人就係隻豬，當個男人同女人行埋，就命不久矣。<br />\n<br />\n粵語「行埋」即「上」，一「上」就死，十足劏豬之凳，剋夫如此之女人，都咪話唔得人驚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港最佳例子係咪梁成恩未婚妻張芝玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中出左留低個遺腹子 俾條女剋死個男嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歷史會為第一代白警平反<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wgcYmZ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwgcYmZ6.jpg&h=756432d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/prK4hyO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FprK4hyO.jpg&h=d2b60479&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b124889f9774e29a45a1891282fbc37862f4564","tid":2284063,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e93d6fc704ee26f6a875e5e28ef3c0836431c7","tid":2284063,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbde865d17d246b7f60ef86f69938f2fe4fd701a","tid":2284063,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"